room_title: Escape room "I.R.I.S." by Puzzah! in Denver
room_description: In another universe, time machines are everywhere. They make life exciting, but they use a toxic fuel that is poisoning the planet. A brilliant artificial intelligence named I.R.I.S. has a plan and needs a resourceful team of time agents to carry it out. Are you prepared to jump back in time to save the world?
